 "lrc": "[00:04.16]Old stops\n[00:06.24]New eyes\n[00:07.44]Blue light\n[00:08.40]Passing by\n[00:09.76]Window black\n[00:10.48]Face in glass\n[00:12.16]I see me\n[00:13.20]Then I pass\n[00:14.64]Downtown\n[00:15.92]Uptown\n[00:16.48]Under every sound\n[00:17.44]I keep floating\n[00:20.56]I keep finding ground\n[00:22.96]And everybody’s going somewhere\n[00:25.52]Everybody’s holding something\n[00:26.72]Everybody looks so tired\n[00:28.80]Still the city keeps on humming\n[00:31.68]So I let the rhythm hold me\n[00:35.12]Let the tunnel pull me through\n[00:37.76]Every station feels familiar\n[00:40.16]But I’m waking up brand new\n[00:42.40]Between the stations\n[00:43.59]I can breathe again\n[00:45.26]I can breathe again\n[00:46.50]I can breathe\n[00:47.43]Between the stations\n[00:48.36]I come back to me\n[00:49.76]Come back to me\n[00:51.04]Come back to me\n[00:52.16]Lights keep flashing\n[00:54.72]Hearts keep passing\n[00:54.78]Still I breathe\n[00:55.55]Still I breathe\n[00:56.68]Between the stations\n[00:57.77]I can breathe again\n[00:59.22]I can breathe again\n[01:00.67]I can breathe\n[01:01.76]Breathe in\n[01:03.04]Breathe out\n[01:03.92]Train goes underground\n[01:29.92]Breathe in\n[01:30.08]Breathe out\n[01:30.25]Lost but I’m found\n[01:30.57]Breathe in\n[01:30.73]Breathe out\n[01:30.90]Let the night slow down\n[01:31.30]Breathe in\n[01:31.47]Breathe out\n[01:31.63]I’m here right now\n[01:31.95]A train to Brooklyn\n[01:32.24]A dream to Queens\n[01:33.52]Bronx in the rhythm\n[01:34.88]Manhattan in the steam\n[01:36.16]Someone’s got roses\n[01:37.12]Someone’s got rain\n[01:38.32]Someone’s got nothing\n[01:39.28]But a song for the pain\n[01:40.80]I don’t need answers\n[01:42.00]I don’t need signs\n[01:43.20]Just one more breath\n[01:44.08]And a little more time\n[01:45.92]And everybody’s changing cars\n[01:48.00]Everybody’s chasing daylight\n[01:50.96]Everybody’s half a scar\n[01:51.62]Glowing under tunnel-white\n[01:54.88]So I let the rhythm hold me\n[01:58.35]